Package: ggmlR
Type: Package
Title: GGML Tensor Operations for Machine Learning
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yuri", "Baramykov",
    email = "lbsbmsu@mail.ru",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Yuri Baramykov [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yuri Baramykov <lbsbmsu@mail.ru>
Description: Provides R bindings to the GGML library for efficient machine 
    learning tensor operations on CPU. Supports basic tensor operations 
    including element-wise addition and multiplication. GGML is a tensor 
    library focused on performance and portability for machine learning.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
